  • public class TH_ISO14443_4_Maxim_MAX66040
extends TH_ISO14443_4_Maxim
    Class for ISO14443-4 transponder MAX66040 of manufacturer MAXIM.
    This class supports only addressed and selected mode in Host-Mode
    .
    Description:
    High-level class for easy-to-use Transponder specific communication. See ITagGroup for additional information.
    Detailed description about the command interface can be found in:
    - Product Datasheet for MAX66040 from MAXIM

    Note: Programmers should be familiar with the ISO 14443 standards.
